insights: Model has high average error (MAE=12.27, MAPE=39.57%)

data.summary: Naive forecast model shows poor performance with 39.57% average error and cannot reliably predict rice production/export for the next 5 years. The model systematically overpredicts and has no explanatory power (R-squared=-inf).
